{"header":"<h1>Module <code><span>Union_Find_Lattice.Classic</span></code></h1>","type":"documentation","uses_katex":false,"breadcrumbs":[{"name":"Index","href":"../../../index.html","kind":"leaf-page"},{"name":"union-find-lattice","href":"../../index.html","kind":"page"},{"name":"Union_Find_Lattice","href":"../index.html","kind":"module"},{"name":"Classic","href":"#","kind":"module"}],"toc":[],"source_anchor":null,"preamble":"<p>Classic union-find lattice with no extensions (values or labels)</p>","content":"<div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-ArrayWithCopy\"><a href=\"#module-ArrayWithCopy\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"ArrayWithCopy/index.html\">ArrayWithCopy</a></span><span>\u000A  (<a href=\"ArrayWithCopy/argument-1-Config/index.html\">Config</a> : <a href=\"../Parameters/module-type-ARRAY_CONFIG/index.html\">Parameters.ARRAY_CONFIG</a>)\u000A  (<a href=\"ArrayWithCopy/argument-2-Node/index.html\">Node</a> : <a href=\"../Parameters/module-type-NODE_WITH_COMPARE/index.html\">Parameters.NODE_WITH_COMPARE</a>) : \u000A  <a href=\"../Sig/module-type-UNION_FIND_LATTICE/index.html\">Sig.UNION_FIND_LATTICE</a> <span class=\"keyword\">with</span> <span><span class=\"keyword\">type</span> <a href=\"../Sig/module-type-UNION_FIND_LATTICE/index.html#type-node\">node</a> = <a href=\"ArrayWithCopy/argument-2-Node/index.html#type-t\">Node.t</a></span></span></code></div><div class=\"spec-doc\"><p>Reference implementation: this implements union-find as a mutable array. <b>Warning:</b> it is NOT persistent, but provides a <a href=\"../Sig/module-type-UNION_FIND_LATTICE/index.html#val-copy\" title=\"Sig.UNION_FIND_LATTICE.copy\"><code>copy</code></a> function</p></div></div><div class=\"odoc-spec\"><div class=\"spec module anchored\" id=\"module-PatriciaTree\"><a href=\"#module-PatriciaTree\" class=\"anchor\"></a><code><span><span class=\"keyword\">module</span> <a href=\"PatriciaTree/index.